YubiKey U2F & PAM Authentication Plugin for OpenVPN

Requirements:
- Python3
- https://github.com/thesparklabs/u2fval
- pip packages - python-u2flib-server pam flask flask-sqlalchemy cachelib u2fval-client

This plugin uses YubiKey U2F and PAM to authenticate a user.

Knowledge Base guide @ https://sparklabs.com/support/kb/article/yubikey-u2f-two-factor-authentication-with-openvpn-and-viscosity/

Plugin is awaiting PR acceptance for support, hopefully from OpenVPN 2.5 onwards
Pre-modified OpenVPN available from SparkLabs PPA - https://launchpad.net/~sparklabs